file_content.text: Let's get outta here while the getting's still good.
You played that real smooth. Didn't know you had it in you.
Guess the gundark's out of the bag now, huh?
We're so close to the admiral, I can taste it.
Pirrell's gonna be real happy with us.
This job never gets any easier, does it?
So far, so good. I think Pirrell is starting to trust us.
That was nasty. Glad we're still alive.
We've definitely made an impression on our new friend.
Let's see what else Pirrell wants us to do.
This job's gonna be easy, right? You wouldn't walk me into a death trap, right?
What are we waiting for? Let's introduce ourselves to Lieutenant Major Pirrell.
We'd better check the ship's holo and find out who your target is.
